===Grand Forks Qualifier=== The Grand Forks qualifier was held at the [[Grand Forks Curling Club]] in [[Grand Forks, North Dakota|Grand Forks]], [[North Dakota]]. It will be held in a triple knockout format. Two teams qualified directly to the Nationals, and four teams qualified to the Challenge Round.<ref name="berth allocations"/> The team skipped by [[John Shuster]] qualified directly to the Nationals by winning the A Event, and the team skipped by [[Owen Sampson]] qualified directly to the Nationals by winning the B Event.<ref name="qualteams"/> Teams skipped by [[Eric Fenson]], [[Peter Stolt]], [[Ryan Berg]], and [[Todd Birr]] qualified to the Challenge Round.<ref name="CRteams"/>
