===Green Bay Qualifier=== The Green Bay qualifier was held at the [[Green Bay Curling Club]] in [[Green Bay, Wisconsin|Green Bay]], [[Wisconsin]]. It was held in a round robin format. At the conclusion of the round robin, one team qualified directly to the Nationals, and two teams qualified to the Challenge Round.<ref name="berth allocations"/> The team skipped by [[Blake Morton]] qualified directly to the Nationals,<ref name="qualteams"/> while the teams skipped by [[John Benton (curler)|John Benton]] and [[Mike Farbelow]] qualified to the Challenge Round.<ref name="CRteams"/>
